{"tid":142382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"闖男友寓所 失業女領呔上吊亡","createTime":"2017-03-03T16:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T17:23:11.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a73f6689764a84d41be80460e5dd9b7f03ed71f","tid":142382,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"荃灣寶雲匯10座，傍晚6時許，一名25歲姓黃女子用後備鎖匙進入男友家中，當時屋內無其他人，她取出一條領呔在睡房內上吊自殺，男友的父母剛巧回家揭發，慌忙報案。消防接報到場後，將女事主救下，交由救護車送往搶救，惜終告不治。警方正調查其自殺原因。據悉，死者最近失業。"},{"pid":"7b252e468673f5923e8715bec269a5319eba3976","tid":142382,"uid":26399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:49:17.000Z","msg":"好似差唔多時間又係荃灣有個男做銀行經理跳樓"},{"pid":"d8e0c8f72f69bbe27e47d9987cf4fa048c3059bb","tid":142382,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:51:05.000Z","msg":"變凶宅"},{"pid":"9bdf641071728b6a553cb403f83f442b9d36856f","tid":142382,"uid":43721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T17:18:15.000Z","msg":"一拍兩散<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3196972da7f87196391ebce5d6bffe5b412527","tid":142382,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T17:23:11.000Z","msg":"當佢係單位時未斷氣，去到醫院先死<br />\n仲算唔算凶宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：冇樓"}]}